		"name": "OWASP Top 10:2021 \u2014 Web Application Security",
		"version": "2.0.0",
		"description": "Comprehensive compliance framework enforcing the OWASP Top 10:2021 web application security risks. Covers injection, broken access control, cryptographic failures, insecure design, security misconfiguration, vulnerable components, authentication failures, logging deficiencies, and SSRF through dataflow, AST, regex, import-graph, and file-level checks.",
